l test helper plugins implement `ScoreExtensions()`:\n- **pkg/scheduler/testing/framework/fake_plugins.go** - `FakePreScoreAndScorePlugin.ScoreExtensions()`\n- **pkg/scheduler/testing/framework/fake_extender.go** - `node2PrioritizerPlugin.ScoreExtensions()`\n\n## Test Files (19 files total)\nAll test files reference `ScoreExtensions` through either method implementations or direct calls to `ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()`:\n\n1. **test/integration/scheduler/plugins/plugins_test.go** - `ScorePlugin` and `ScoreWithNormalizePlugin` test plugins\n2. **pkg/scheduler/schedule_one_test.go** - Multiple test plugins with `ScoreExtensions()` implementations\n3. **pkg/scheduler/framework/runtime/framework_test.go** - Test plugins: `TestScoreWithNormalizePlugin`, `TestScorePlugin`, `TestPlugin`\n4. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/interpodaffinity/scoring_test.go** - Calls `ScorePlugin.ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()` (lines 813, 976)\n5. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/nodeaffinity/node_affinity_test.go** - Calls `ScorePlugin.ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()` (line 1224)\n6. **pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/tainttoleration/taint_toleration_test.go** - Calls `ScorePlugin.ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore()` (line 261)\n\n## Supporting Files\n**pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/helper/normalize_score.go** and **normalize_score_test.go** define and test the `DefaultNormalizeScore()` helper function used by plugins implementing `ScoreExtensions`.\n\n## Total Files Requiring Updates\nAt least **21 files** will require updates to rename `ScoreExtensions` to `ScoreNormalizer` and the associated accessor method from `ScoreExtensions()` to `ScoreNormalizer()`."
